## Checklist (same as CI)

- Pre-commit: fully passing run (not ‚Äúmostly‚Äù fixed).
- Tests: full `make test` green.
- PR: `make test-diff-coverage` green after `git fetch origin`.
- PR materials: only after user confirmation; include trailers when drafting commits.
